thread.title: BRIEF-Jiangsu Transimage Technology sees FY 2018 Q1 net profit up 30 pct to 50 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Jiangsu Transimage Technology sees FY 2018 Q1 net profit up 30 pct to 50 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - jiangsu transimage technology co ltd

text:
Jan 24(Reuters) - Jiangsu Transimage Technology Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2018 Q1 net profit to increase by 30 percent to 50 percent, or to be 28.8 million yuan to 32.2 million yuan
* Says FY 2017 Q1 net profit was 22.2 million yuan
* The main reason for the forecast is improved performance of laptop keyboard business Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/oukp7G Further company coverage: (Beijing Headline News)
